OL,6,FHe then fled and was driving an Audi
OL,7,FRS3 six days later when he collided
OL,8,Fwith a Vauxhall Corsa being driven by
OL,9,Fa 61-year-old woman in South Kirkby,
OL,10,FWest Yorkshire.
OL,12,FShe suffered serious injuries in the
OL,13,Fcrash.
OL,15,FFlowers, of Masefield Road, Rotherham,
OL,16,Fran off from the scene. He was
OL,17,Feventually arrested more than three
OL,18,Fmonths later, on 2 November.
