OL,3,CDriver who seriously injured two in
OL,4,Ccrashes days apart jailed
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,7,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving as well as failing to stop and
OL,9,Ffailing to report an accident.
OL,11,FFlowers was jailed for six-and-a-half
OL,12,Fyears at Sheffield Crown Court.
OL,14,FThe court heard the crash involving Mr
OL,15,FLloyd sent his car 60m along Rotherham
OL,16,FRoad, where it collided with a wall.
OL,18,FThe driver's door was ripped off and
OL,19,Fhe was thrown from the vehicle.
