OL,6,FMr Lloyd continues to need constant
OL,7,Fcare, South Yorkshire Police said.
OL,9,FSgt John Taylor said: "Joshua
OL,10,Fsustained significant life changing
OL,11,Finjuries during the collision and our
OL,12,Fthoughts remain very much with him and
OL,13,Fhis family today.
OL,15,F"It has been a very difficult period
OL,16,Fof time for them as their lives have
OL,17,Fbeen changed forever by this incident."
OL,19,FFollowing the incident Flowers was
OL,20,Fdriven from the scene by 30-year-old
OL,21,FHannah Costello and went on the run.
