OL,6,FHe caused the second crash after
OL,7,Ffailing to stop for police.
OL,9,FFlowers was eventually arrested by
OL,10,Fofficers at an address in the
OL,11,FShiregreen area of Sheffield.
OL,13,FSgt Taylor added: "I am pleased that
OL,14,FFlowers is now behind bars where he
OL,15,Fcan cause no further harm to our
OL,16,Fcommunities. We will not tolerate
OL,17,Fdrivers who deliberately ignore the
OL,18,Frules of the road and put innocent
OL,19,Fpeople at risk."
